{
  "texts": [
    "Leveraging AI technology can automate this process, offering significant benefits in terms of efficiency and accuracy.",
    "• Automated business impact analysis-Business impact analysis is a vital method for identifying essential functions and applications within the business environment, assessing the potential consequences of cybersecurity incidents.",
    "To streamline this process, AI techniques can be employed to automate the business impact analysis.",
    "This can be achieved by evaluating economic risks associated with known attack vectors or by calculating the feasibility of threats and the probability of high-impact security events affecting critical business areas.",
    "By leveraging AI, organizations can enhance the efficiency and accuracy of their business impact analysis, enabling them to make informed decisions and prioritize their cybersecurity efforts effectively."
  ]
}